    "details": "Goal progress tracking card with multi-segment animated progress bar showing completed, in-flight, and remaining work. Features gradient fills, animated diagonal stripes for in-progress tasks, circular thumb indicator, and dynamic status messaging. Built with shadcn/ui Card components with full dark mode support using CSS custom properties. Perfect for fitness apps, project management dashboards, goal tracking platforms, and any interface requiring visual progress indicators with detailed status feedback."
